<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.10">
<l>ōṭa vōṭak kiṇki ṇika ḷolikku mōcaip pāṇi yālē</l>
<l>pāṭip pāṭi varukiṉ ṟāyaip paṟpa nāpa ṉeṉṟi runtē</l>
<l>ṉāṭi yāṭi yacainta caintiṭ ṭataṉuk kēṟṟa kūttai yāṭi</l>
<l>yōṭi yōṭip pōyvi ṭātē yutta mānī mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was thinking, “[He is] Padmanabha,” about you</l>
<l>who comes singing with songs and melodies</l>
<l>and ankle bells that jingle as you run.</l>
<l>Supreme One! Dancing and dancing and [then] become exhausted,</l>
<l rend="indent">if [you] consider [doing] that,</l>
<l>Do not leave and go off running and dancing [your] dance!</l>
<l>You [should] drink from [my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
